Bill Nestell https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bill_Nestell 0 Bill Nestell (3 March 1893 – 18 October 1966) was an American film actor. He appeared in over 100 films between 1926 and 1950. He was born in California, and died in Bishop, California from a heart attack. Bill_Nestell ( 3_March_1893 – 18_October_1966 ) was an_American_film_actor .
